Pack your bags, you could win inter-island airfare for two and a 4-night stay at @thewestinmaui with our Maui Caramacs Passport to Paradise Sweepstakes!
 
Here’s how to join the fun: 🍫 Visit participating retailers during the times listed below
🧡 Find the Hawaiian Host team in-store to get your passport stamped (passports will be available on 6/28, 7/5, and 7/12) ✍🏼 Collect three stamps for one entry or all six for a BONUS entry 📍Turn in your passport to the Hawaiian Host team at Don Don Donki in Kapolei on July 26, 2025
 
Participating Retailers:
• Foodland Ala Moana — June 28, 10 AM to 2PM
• Walmart Keeaumoku — June 28, 10 AM to 2PM
• Longs Ala Moana — July 5, 10 AM to 2 PM
• Don Quijote Kaheka — July 12, 10 AM to 2 PM
• Waikiki Market — July 19, 10 AM to 2 PM
• Don Don Donki Kapolei — July 26, 10 AM to 2 PM

No purchase necessary to enter or win. Open to legal residents of Hawaii, age 18 or older. Click the link in our bio for official rules.

We’re so honored to welcome you both to the Hawaiian Host ‘ohana 🤎 Throughout this journey, you’ve inspired us—and many others—with your aloha, authenticity, and humility. We can’t wait for all that’s to come as you carry forward this incredible legacy and represent both Hawaiian Host and our islands.

For over a decade, Kawehi Kamakele has been the face of our iconic AlohaMacs chocolates. With kindness, grace, and aloha, she doesn’t just represent us — she connects people to Hawai‘i 🤎  Now, it’s your turn to be the New Face of AlohaMacs! There’s only ONE WEEK left to apply, so get your application in by May 4th and spread the word to your friends and ‘ohana! 
—— 
NO PURCHASE NECESSARY. Open to legal residents of Hawaiʻi, who are 18 or older and the age of majority in their state, excluding Sponsor’s employees, immediate family and household members. Enter by completing and submitting an online registration form with a fifteen (15) to thirty (30) second audition video that meets the listed requirements between 4/8/25 and 5/4/25. See Official Rules for judging process and criteria. Grand Prize, First Runner Up Prize and Third Runner Up Prize available. ARV of grand prize: $15,090.00. For a copy of the Official Rules, visit www.HawaiianHost.com. Sponsor: Hawaiian Host Group, 851 Fort Street Mall, Suite 200, Honolulu, HI 96813.   #HawaiianHost #NewFacesofAlohaMacs #Legacy #Hawaii
